{"tid":1017062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【支持填海】美聯黃靜怡：填海改善本港住屋質素","createTime":"2019-02-11T08:07:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T08:20:41.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"975f1ab54e95ac3f83df1d335f4b4d07a9703ebf","tid":1017062,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T08:07:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20190211/s00011/8d620d220d8ad7dc43837170ba8ffa28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20190211%2Fs00011%2F8d620d220d8ad7dc43837170ba8ffa28.jpg&h=07ef9b06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1549861411672&amp;issue=20190211\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantp2.php%3Fnode%3D1549861411672%26issue%3D20190211&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu14WZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=39cba207\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1549861411672&amp;issue=20190211</a><br />\n<br />\n美聯集團（1200）今日舉行2019年新春團拜，美聯集團副主席黃靜怡表示，香港過去40年樓價有升有跌，但整體仍錄得升勢，雖然早前香港樓價有調整，狗年更價量齊跌，惟香港基調好、投資流動性強，加上其它投資工具波動，中長線仍看好本地樓市發展。<br />\n<br />\n對於增加本港住宅供應，黃認為，填海屬於好選擇，有助香港增加供應及改善住屋質素，過往本港不少土地及區域是來自填海，因此長遠用填海策略對住宅及商業發展都好。黃建議，今年入市買家要「勤、精、快」，買樓收租人士要留意本港中長線發展。<br />\n<br />\n記者：謝穎怡"},{"pid":"3f7ec379d509cc5cba77b5e74a7f65651392e377","tid":1017062,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T08:11:02.000Z","msg":"中原施慧勤 VS 美聯黃靜怡<br />\n <br />\n施慧勤<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2018/12/1545219663_Dj-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2018%2F12%2F1545219663_Dj-1280w.jpg&h=9d29fcd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃靜怡<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.propnews.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/aw-390.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.propnews.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F12%2Faw-390.jpg&h=1869a2c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n施慧勤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黃靜怡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c1aabd3b1d955b23d66f12bbd8f9acd3cdf6762","tid":1017062,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T08:14:58.000Z","msg":"填撚完咪又係起奈米樓，有咩分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d803a245de5416de0465d33b7e4743b032a1198","tid":1017062,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0c1aabd3b1d955b23d66f12bbd8f9acd3cdf6762","tid":1017062,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T08:14:58.000Z","msg":"填撚完咪又係起奈米樓，有咩分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T08:15:46.000Z","msg":"納米，打錯自膠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66ceb29675fc40af6fa286962b69d2808014a84","tid":1017062,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T08:16:20.000Z","msg":"改善地產經紀收入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"782cfbc611cc5d4eb439f22b31c26034291d8f1a","tid":1017062,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a66ceb29675fc40af6fa286962b69d2808014a84","tid":1017062,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T08:16:20.000Z","msg":"改善地產經紀收入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T08:17:06.000Z","msg":"地產相關公司一致支持<br />\n<br />\n錢銀攸關"},{"pid":"2f8a14afffda4318652513ccb47d7382247f3f72","tid":1017062,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quo